---
title: Shrimp and Veggie Burrito Bowls with Plant-Based Protein and DIY Salsa
description: Get ready for burrito vibes but minus the mess! Hearty sweet potatoes, shrimp and plant-based protein served on a bed of pepper-onion rice make for a satisfying supper. This bowl is made even better with two tasty toppers: lime crema and DIY salsa!

